title: person of interest S02E14 great scene
author: Pigueza F. Strawson
comment: Wow, since when was there a data catalog of every little speck of the McLaren MP4-12C? That is brilliant.

Do you know what car you’re hacking? A McLaren MP4-12C. A $150,000 (current; $250,000 new) supercar with a 3.8L twin turbo V8 that makes 616 horsepower, gets the car to 60 in 3.1 seconds and tops out at 204 mph. The McLaren’s quick supercar brakes are what helped stop the supercar.
